ContentDesc_Chateau Cosmea: Long ago, on the far shore of the Source, a great palace was built by the elves─the Grand Cosmos, an edifice of such magnitude it was said to inspire envy in both the heavens for which it was named and the flowers that pervade its boundless gardens. As with so many wonders of the world that once was, its radiance quickly faded in the wake of the Flood, its halls falling silent, the throne sitting empty. That is, until the palace was given new purpose when a mage claimed it as their sanctuary, their only company being solace, solitude, and the legion of familiars barring entrance to any foolish enough to seek an audience.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23406_Text: Come, my lovelies! There is filth that wants for cleaning!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23407_Text: Such pernicious stains, you are. No matter...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23408_Text: Ugh! Insufferable, the lot of you. I will spare you, but only this once. Now leave me be!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23410_Text: Ssem a tahw, ssem a tahw! Swish-swish-aroo!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23411_Text: Come, then, little ones. Let me show you the delights of my garden.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23412_Text: The time has come to play, my children. Hearken to my melody.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23413_Text: Grow, my children, grow! Show them the glory of your splendor!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23415_Text: Go, Lugus. Turn them to ash. I care not how.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23416_Text: Yes, set them alight with your undying flames. Burn bright until they are naught but cinders!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23419_Text: From ageless sleep, I bid thee rise!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23420_Text: Bring unto them a swift demise!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23421_Text: I call forth blades to run them through!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23423_Text: With wings of dreams, I bar thy path.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23424_Text: I conjure forth the garden's wrath.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23425_Text: Hold them fast with thorn and vine.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23426_Text: To death's embrace their souls consign.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23427_Text: I summon thee from flesh of stone.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23428_Text: Seize the intruders who besmirch thy hall!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23430_Text: Should you value your lives, you will quit this place at once. Now, begone with you!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23431_Text: Look how they make a mess of my floors! Swish and flick, my lovelies. Swish and flick!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23432_Text: If you insist on making a mess of my palace, then you leave me no choice...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23433_Text: Still you press onward? How foolish.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23434_Text: Leannan sith! These cretins have sullied the sanctity of your garden. They must be dealt with!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23435_Text: The garden is ruined. Ruined! Mark my words─you will pay for this!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23436_Text: With wings of dreams to grind their bones.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23437_Text: Why do you persist? Why will you not leave me be!?
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23438_Text: And by King's judgment see them fall.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_23439_Text: I see you cannot be dissuaded from your misguided path. A pity...
